# House Prediction Prices Algorithm - ML
 
A machine learning project that predicts California house prices using the XGBoost Regressor algorithm.
 
## Dataset
California Housing Dataset from scikit-learn, containing 20,640 entries with 8 features:
- MedInc, HouseAge, AveRooms, AveBedrms, Population, AveOccup, Latitude, Longitude
## Model
- Algorithm: XGBoost Regressor
- R² score on training data: 0.94
- R² score on test data: 0.83
## Libraries Used
- numpy, pandas, matplotlib, seaborn, scikit-learn, xgboost
 
